      • SCHEMA_BATCH_ENABLED

        protected static boolean SCHEMA_BATCH_ENABLED
        The scan operator can return an empty schema batch as the first batch. But, this broke multiple operators that do not handle this case. So, it is turned off for now. Tests that verified the empty batch use this flag to disable that checking.
